snippet.title: RIYANA's COOKBOOK
snippet.description:
Hi, I am Riyana Ameer 
Riyana’s cookbook is a collection of my successful cooking experiments..captured and explained in simple understandable manner..

I am crazy and passionate about cooking..i take small scale orders for parties..The positive feedback i get has been a motivation to go ahead..Compiling all the good recipes and bringing it forward to public has been my dream since i started my cooking journey..I am sure that u will all find it interesting and delicious..

Pls like, share & subscribe my channel
